{"id": "1474749730570371245", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "type": 0, "author_id": "464582708325122049", "author_name": "megidola.", "author_bot": false, "content": "I have to say that I greatly dislike the Reality Verge system.\n||I am currently doing Chapter 7 right now and in one of the stages, William just casually says something like \"as we have seen with the Ramona: Timeworn incident it seems she can't cross the Storm Wall due to her connection with Tawil\" and I had just sit there and nod along as if I knew what he was talking about. Luckily since then I was able to unlock it and play it so I can now continue chapter 7. I am trying to loosely follow the recommended timeline pictured in the attached image but it is impossible as I do not have enough Verges, so I have only done Daff's, Sorel's and G-Ramona so far. This game would probably benefit from automatically unlocking side stories that are relevant to the main plot so people can even begin to experience the story as it was intended instead of just having to guess what happened in between story chapters. The fact that N is introduced in a easy to miss side story is also something I find wild. But I'm still at chapter 7 so no spoilers please, just wanted get my thoughts out there||", "timestamp": "2026-02-21T12:48:55.293000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-02-21T12:49:57.999000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1474749730172043364", "filename": "SPOILER_Morimens_Story_Timeline.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 49836, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1326453763355185215/1474749730172043364/SPOILER_Morimens_Story_Timeline.png?ex=69cd1437&is=69cbc2b7&hm=b4753e277e5f3387fc054f0e6470439c763a104589373aaecba38d50eef10a16&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
